rep_input: Patient HR+/HER2- progressed after CDK4/6; what key label-based caveats should I discuss?
model_output: For HR+/HER2- patients who progressed after CDK4/6, label-based options depend on prior endocrine and chemo exposure, performance status, and visceral involvement. It's important to review the EMA SmPC for each therapy to ensure on-label use and discuss expected efficacy and safety in this context. Please send the relevant SmPC sections by email for precise reference.
